Questions? Answers.

How does GeniusTag work without batteries?

GeniusTag uses NFC (Near Field Communication) technology, the same tech in contactless payments. When someone taps their phone to the tag, the phone's electromagnetic field powers the tag and reads the stored data. No batteries needed, ever.

Do finders need to download an app?

No. When someone finds your pet and taps their phone on the tag, your profile opens directly in their web browser. No app download required. This makes the connection instant and friction-free.

Is there a subscription fee?

Never. You pay once and your pet is protected for life. No monthly fees, no annual renewals, no hidden charges. Your $24.99 purchase includes lifetime access to unlimited profile updates.

What if my phone number changes?

Simply log into the GeniusPet app and update your contact information. Changes take effect instantly. You can update your phone number, address, emergency contacts, and pet details as often as needed.

Is the tag waterproof?

Yes. GeniusTag is designed to withstand rain, swimming, baths, and everything your adventurous pet encounters. The durable construction protects the NFC chip in all weather conditions.

What's your return policy?

We offer a 90-day money-back guarantee, no questions asked. If GeniusTag isn't right for your pet, contact us within 90 days for a full refund. We're confident you'll love it.
